Comment: 10,0:00:04.29,0:00:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I can't let Croix go unchecked any longer.{## more of a suggestion tbh}
Comment: 10,0:00:08.64,0:00:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}She must be stopped...
Comment: 10,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Before it's too late.
